{"article_id":"hsEVDUnelQxPKJuC","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi would not commit on Wednesday to sending the articles of impeachment against President Donald Trump to the Republican-held Senate , a surprise move","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"that injects new uncertainty into Congress ' timeline of the President 's trial in the chamber .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"`` That would have been our intention ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"but we 'll see what happens over there , ''","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"Pelosi said at a post-impeachment vote news conference Wednesday night","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"when asked about sending over the articles .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Some progressives have urged Democratic leaders to withhold the articles","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"until Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell , a Kentucky Republican , agrees to the parameters for the Senate trial","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"that Democrats have called for ,","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"as well as agreeing to bring in firsthand witnesses like acting White House chief of staff Mick Mulvaney","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"to testify .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"On Thursday morning , Pelosi used her weekly news conference","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"to express her concern","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"over having a fair trial in the Senate ,","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"while the Founding Fathers had anticipated the possibility of a rogue President ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"`` I do n't think","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"they suspected","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"that we could have a rogue president and a rogue leader in the Senate at the same time . ''","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"`` The next thing for us will be when we see the process","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"that is set forth in the Senate ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"then we 'll know the number of managers","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"that we may have to go forward","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"and who we will choose , ''","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Pelosi said .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"`` That 's what I said last night ,","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"that 's what I 'm saying now . ''","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"While Pelosi 's comments create a new level of confusion to the impeachment procedure and timeline ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"it 's unclear what the specific advantages there would be to withholding to the articles of impeachment from a Senate trial .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Republicans argue","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"there is no benefit","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"in delaying something","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"they do n't want to spend time on anyway .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"When McConnell was asked this week about articles","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"not being sent over ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"he told reporters ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"`` I 'm in no hurry . ''","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"But Pelosi 's comments have also angered some Republicans in the Senate .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"GOP Sen. Lindsey Graham of South Carolina , said Thursday","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"he was outraged .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"`` What they 're proposing","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"-- to not send the articles for disposition to the Senate","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"after being passed to the House --","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"is incredibly dangerous , ''","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"`` This is a land","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"-- uncharted waters , constitutionally , ''","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"Graham told reporters .","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"`` I just know this ,","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"that this matters to the future of the country .","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"We can not have a system","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"where the House impeaches the president ,","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"tells the Senate how to conduct the trial ,","depth":15},{"id":54,"text":"holds the articles of impeachment over the president 's head at a time of their choosing","depth":16},{"id":55,"text":"to unleash them . ''","depth":16},{"id":56,"text":"McConnell has openly sparred with his Democratic counterpart , Minority Leader Chuck Schumer of New York , over the format of the Senate trial .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"Earlier this week , McConnell rejected Schumer 's call","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"for four witnesses to testify .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"On the Senate floor Thursday morning , McConnell described Pelosi 's delay","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"in sending the articles of impeachment to the Senate","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"as a sign","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"that `` House Democrats may be too afraid to even transmit their shoddy work product to the Senate . ''","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"Pelosi said Wednesday night","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"that House Democrats will make the decision `` as a group '' on when to send the articles to the Senate .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"House Majority Whip James Clyburn said Thursday","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"that he is in favor of withholding the articles","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"`` until we can get some assurances from","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"( McConnell )","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"that he is going to allow for a fair and impartial trial to take place . ''","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"Asked by CNN 's John Berman on `` New Day ''","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"how long he is willing to wait for that assurance ,","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"the South Carolina Democrat replied :","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"`` As long as it takes .","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"Even if he does n't come around to committing to a fair trial ,","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"keep those articles here . ''","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"House Judiciary Chairman Jerry Nadler , a New York Democrat","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"whose committee authored the articles ,","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"said","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"that they `` need to be sent in due course . ''","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"When asked Thursday morning","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"if the articles should be held forever ,","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"Nadler told CNN ,","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"`` I would doubt that .","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"Beyond that , I do n't know . ''","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"The issue did not come up extensively at a closed-door caucus meeting Thursday morning among House Democrats ,","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"according to multiple attendees ,","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"and several members said","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"they need to know the parameters of the Senate trial","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"before picking impeachment managers for the Senate trial ,","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"because they may need different skill-sets","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"There are procedural concerns","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"behind not sending the articles to the Senate on Wednesday night immediately after the vote .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"Among them :","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"Democrats ca n't send the articles Wednesday night","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"because the Senate would have to take it up Thursday ,","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"blocking votes on two spending packages","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"that must pass before week 's end","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"to avoid a government shutdown .","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"In the coming days , the House must also name impeachment managers for the Senate 's trial , another step","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"Pelosi was not ready to make Wednesday night .","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"`` We can not name managers","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"until we see what the process is on the Senate side ,","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"and we hope","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"that will be soon , ''","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"Pelosi said .","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"`` So far we have n't seen anything","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"that looks fair to us ,","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"so hopefully it will be fair . ''","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":217,"left":0,"right":216,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":216,"left":119,"right":215,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":119,"left":114,"right":118,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":110,"right":113,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":111,"right":112,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":112,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":7,"right":117,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":115,"right":116,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":115,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":215,"left":134,"right":214,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":121,"right":133,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":12,"right":120,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":125,"right":132,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":15,"right":124,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":124,"left":16,"right":123,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":123,"left":17,"right":122,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":122,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":132,"left":130,"right":131,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS